<h1>Help control the pet population. Have your pets spayed or neutered. ~ Bob Barker</h1>

<h2>Dogs that need to be spayed or neutered!</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each dogs}}
    {{#unless spayed}}
      {{> dogs/dog-block spayed=true}}
    {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Dogs that are spayed or neutered!</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each dogs}}
    {{#if spayed}}
      {{> dogs/dog-block spayed=false}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Add a Dog</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Dog Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="spayed">Spayed?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="spayed" value="1" checked> Spayed!<br>
    <input type="radio" name="spayed" value="0"> Not Spayed
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Dog</button>
</form>
